  <name>Pinba Engine</name>
  <summary>Real-time statistics storage engine for MySQL and MariaDB</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Pinba is a storage engine for MySQL and MariaDB that collects and
      processes application runtime statistics sent over UDP by Pinba clients,
      most commonly the Pinba PHP extension. It provides real-time, per-request
      performance monitoring and profiling, queried through ordinary SQL,
      without any additional infrastructure.
    </p>
  </description>

